 Nicholas J. Valeriani, 34-Year Johnson & Johnson Veteran, Appointed Chief Executive of West Health 
         










    










 






 











 









Nicholas J. Valeriani, 34-Year Johnson & Johnson Veteran, Appointed Chief Executive of West Health

		  Valeriani to lead Institute, Policy Center, Investment Fund and newly-launched Incubator in West Health's effort to lower health care costsWest Wireless Health Institute renamed West Health Institute to reflect broader scope
		

Aug 15, 2012, 07:00 ET
		  		  														
						 from   West Health 











 
















































 

 






















































 























 























 

 

 
 
 
 







